pageContext.description: length 96.5mm; width edge 52mm; width mouth 37mm; width loop 10.5mm; breadth mouth 35.3mm; depth socket 65mm; depth internal ribs 28mm,Two closely set mouth mouldings of similar proportions; row of three bosses below; are of punchmarks below bosses; remains of casting flash; blade tip hollows; 2 fine internal ribs - slightly irregular; narrow flat bottom; level, but rounded, top to moulding; poss. small casting flaw at edge.
pageContext.patina: Areas of v. dark green - gold brown patina; much obscured by granular light green surface.
pageContext.surface: Edge intact, not particularly sharp; asymmetry poss. due to wear and useage. Light brown and orangey soil adhering.
